            <th>Details</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Type</strong></td>
            <td>Power Shotgun</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Damage</strong></td>
            <td>1500-2000 per shot</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Special Effect</strong></td>
            <td>High damage at close range, +30% close-range damage</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Best For</strong></td>
            <td>Body builds, close-quarters combat</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Location</strong></td>
            <td>Found in a chest during "The Pickup" mission</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p><strong>Why It's Great:</strong> Guts deals massive damage at close range. It's perfect for rushing enemies and clearing rooms quickly. Works best with Body builds that can tank hits.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="weapon-card">
        <h3>5. Yukimura (Smart SMG)</h3>
        <table>
          <tr>
            <th>Category</th>
            <th>Details</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Type</strong></td>
            <td>Smart SMG</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Damage</strong></td>
            <td>120-180 per bullet</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Special Effect</strong></td>
            <td>Very high fire rate, +15% smart weapon damage</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Best For</strong></td>
            <td>Netrunner builds, close-range combat</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Location</strong></td>
            <td>Dropped by a Maelstrom boss during "The Pickup" mission</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p><strong>Why It's Great:</strong> Yukimura has an insane fire rate and smart targeting. It melts enemies at close range and works well with Netrunner builds that need a reliable sidearm.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="weapon-card">
