          <tr>
            <td><strong>Special Effect</strong></td>
            <td>+50% crit damage, +30% attack speed</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Best For</strong></td>
            <td>Melee builds, Reflexes builds</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Location</strong></td>
            <td>Found in a chest on the rooftop during "The Heist" mission</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p><strong>Why It's Great:</strong> Satori is the best melee weapon in the game. It has incredible crit damage and fast attack speed. Perfect for melee-focused builds.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="weapon-card">
        <h3>9. Jyoken (Tech Sword)</h3>
        <table>
          <tr>
