          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Special Effect</strong></td>
            <td>Charged attacks deal AoE damage, +25% tech weapon damage</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Best For</strong></td>
            <td>Tech melee builds, crowd control</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Location</strong></td>
            <td>Dropped by a Maelstrom boss during "The Pickup" mission</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p><strong>Why It's Great:</strong> Jyoken's charged attacks deal AoE damage, making it excellent for crowd control. It works well with tech melee builds that want to clear groups of enemies.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="weapon-card">
        <h3>10. Cradle (Power LMG)</h3>
        <table>
          <tr>
            <th>Category</th>
            <th>Details</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Type</strong></td>
            <td>Power LMG</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Damage</strong></td>
            <td>200-280 per bullet</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Special Effect</strong></td>
