    <section class="by-build">
      <h2>🎯 Best Iconic Weapons by Build</h2>

      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Build</th>
          <th>Best Iconic Weapons</th>
          <th>Why</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Netrunner</strong></td>
          <td>Nue, Yukimura</td>
          <td>Smart weapons let you focus on hacking</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Tech</strong></td>
          <td>Tactician, Shigure, Jyoken</td>
          <td>Tech weapons charge through walls</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Reflexes</strong></td>
          <td>Ashura, Satori</td>
          <td>Fast attacks, headshot bonuses</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Body</strong></td>
          <td>Guts, Cradle</td>
          <td>High damage, sustained fire</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Cool</strong></td>
          <td>Ba Xing Chong, Satori</td>
          <td>Crit bonuses, stealth damage</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="tips">
      <h2>💡 Iconic Weapon Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Don't sell Iconic weapons.</strong> They're unique and can't be found again if you sell them. Keep them in your stash if you're not using them.</li>
        <li><strong>Upgrade them early.</strong> Iconic weapons scale with your level, so upgrade them as soon as you have the materials.</li>
        <li><strong>Mod them properly.</strong> Iconic weapons have extra mod slots. Use them to maximize their potential.</li>
        <li><strong>Check for hidden Iconic weapons.</strong> Some Iconic weapons are in hidden locations or dropped by specific enemies. Explore thoroughly.</li>
        <li><strong>Some are quest rewards.</strong> Certain Iconic weapons are only available as quest rewards. Don't miss these quests.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="final-note">
      <h2>🏆 Final Thoughts</h2>
      <p>Iconic weapons are what make Cyberpunk 2077's combat so satisfying. Each one has its own personality and playstyle. Find the ones that match your build and upgrade them to maximize your effectiveness.</p>
      <p><strong>Next step:</strong> Check out our <a href="/cyberpunk-2077/cyber-psycho-build">Cyber Psycho Build Guide</a> to see how to use Iconic weapons effectively in a complete build.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .guide {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .intro {
    background: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .info-box {
